Node.js + PHP Workers - Naive Bayes Classifier
----------------------------------------------

Node.js worker to asynchronizes PHP workers doing Naive Bayes Classification.


How To Use
----------

Clone the PHP Simple Naive Bayes Classifier below and put into a sub-directory of this repo root named php-bayes.

Copy or symlink ./bayes.php to ./php-bayes/bayes.php

$ node index.js


Dependencies - Node.js
----------------------

* socket.io >= 0.9.0


Dependencies - PHP
------------------
* PHP >= 5.3.0
* Simple Naive Bayes Classifier - https://github.com/tistaharahap/Simple-Naive-Bayes-Classifier-for-PHP
* php-redis Extension - https://github.com/nicolasff/phpredis


